data.description: Welcome to 90 Falling Spring Rd! This all-stone home is nestled back a small lane off Falling Spring Rd, don't go by too fast or you'll miss the turn! Privacy is here! This is a split-level home meaning there is tons of space throughout! Main level features a living room with fireplace and a BRAND NEW KITCHEN by Dick's Cabinetry & Flooring! Beautiful granite counters, new cabinets and a large kitchen island with barstool space! Down a few steps you will find the huge family room that could suit many needs such as a home office, in home learning and more! Off the family room is the laundry room and a full bath. Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms and 1 full bath that is connected to the large, primary bedroom. And finally! The basement! One finished room and one utility room for even more space and storage! Outside, there is a fully fenced yard and back patio with a hot tub! There is plenty of space to roam! Spend winter nights in the hot tub, spring nights in the garden and summer nights listening to the creek. When the trees are in full bloom, it is nice and quiet. The owners are relocating but they've done so much to this place including new windows, metal roof, gutters, downspouts and more!! Come take a look for yourself!
